    <title>基于八卦演化的个人人生与记账模型</title>
    <link href="http://wwdorian.work/2021/06/07/ji-yu-ba-gua-yan-hua-de-ge-ren-ren-sheng-yu-ji-zhang-mo-xing/"/>
    <id>http://wwdorian.work/2021/06/07/ji-yu-ba-gua-yan-hua-de-ge-ren-ren-sheng-yu-ji-zhang-mo-xing/</id>
    <published>2021-06-07T08:48:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-06-07T08:49:04.290Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph LR</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;思&quot;</span><br><span class="line">shaoyang[少阳]</span><br><span class="line">xun[巽]</span><br><span class="line">kan[坎]</span><br><span class="line">shaoyang --&gt; xun &amp; kan</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;神&quot;</span><br><span class="line">taiyang[太阳]</span><br><span class="line">dui[兑]</span><br><span class="line">qian[乾]</span><br><span class="line">taiyang --&gt; dui &amp; qian</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;谋&quot;</span><br><span class="line">shaoyin[少阴]</span><br><span class="line">zhen[震]</span><br><span class="line">li[离]</span><br><span class="line">shaoyin --&gt; zhen &amp; li</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;明&quot;</span><br><span class="line">taiyin[太阴]</span><br><span class="line">gen[艮]</span><br><span class="line">kun[坤]</span><br><span class="line">taiyin --&gt; gen &amp; kun</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">yang[阳]</span><br><span class="line">yin[阴]</span><br><span class="line">yang --&gt; shaoyang &amp; taiyang</span><br><span class="line">yin --&gt; shaoyin &amp; taiyin</span><br><span class="line">wu[吾]</span><br><span class="line">wu --&gt; yang &amp; yin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>阳主内，指精神与灵魂。阴主外，指物质与身体。<br>阳分少阳，分太阳。少阳分巽，分坎。太阳分兑，分乾。<br>阴分少阴，分太阴。少阴分震，分离。太阴分艮，分坤。<br>少阳为思。巽为智，为思显。坎为慧，为思隐。<br>太阳为神。兑为美，为神显。乾为德，为神隐。<br>少阴为谋。震为利，为谋界。离为益，为谋质。<br>太阴为明。艮为行，为明界。坤为交，为明质。<br>智生慧，慧生美，美生德。利养益，益养行，行养交。<br>智利相成，慧益相生，美行相盈，德交相彰。<br>内外俱成，是谓成人。</p><p>人有无智而入慧者，然鲜矣。<br>人有无美而居德者，然罕哉。<br>人有无利而身益者，需固穷。<br>人有无行而心交者，需道同。</p><p>故若人人有成，则此理需广，此善需泛，此心需强，此为需大。<br>人人可学，人人可成。</p><p>即为 ——<br> 智，则需学理，天下之理，尽皆可学，学来而为我所用。<br>慧，则需用理，天下之理，尽皆可用，用来而为我所循。<br>美，则需循善，天下之善，尽皆可循，循来而为我所悟。<br>德，则需悟善，天下之善，尽皆可悟，悟来而为我所行。<br>利，则需鉴位，天下之位，尽皆可鉴，鉴来而为我所取。<br>益，则需取位，天下之位，尽皆可取，取来而为我所择。<br>行，则需择时，天下之时，尽皆可择，择来而为我所合。<br>交，则需合时，天下之时，尽皆可合，合来而为我所学。</p><hr><p>而又 ——<br> 无智何以生慧？无利何以养益？<br>人不可不求智，亦不可不谋利。<br>只又 ——<br> 智为生慧而求，利为养益而谋。<br>可又 ——<br> 无智者无得，无利者无和。<br>故，以智取利。</p><p>取利须知，利者，循环往复。<br>他人之利，今我取之；<br>我今之利，他来用之。<br>而若论利，人之所欲：财，名，权。<br>权名者无有，近道者乎财。</p><p>取财，须知有出有入。无出无以入，无入不得出。<br>故有，以出养入，以入思出。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph LR</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;瞬&quot;</span><br><span class="line">shaoyang[少阳]</span><br><span class="line">xun[巽]</span><br><span class="line">kan[坎]</span><br><span class="line">shaoyang --&gt; xun &amp; kan</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;恒&quot;</span><br><span class="line">taiyang[太阳]</span><br><span class="line">dui[兑]</span><br><span class="line">qian[乾]</span><br><span class="line">taiyang --&gt; dui &amp; qian</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;往&quot;</span><br><span class="line">shaoyin[少阴]</span><br><span class="line">zhen[震]</span><br><span class="line">li[离]</span><br><span class="line">shaoyin --&gt; zhen &amp; li</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">subgraph &quot;复&quot;</span><br><span class="line">taiyin[太阴]</span><br><span class="line">gen[艮]</span><br><span class="line">kun[坤]</span><br><span class="line">taiyin --&gt; gen &amp; kun</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">yang[阳]</span><br><span class="line">yin[阴]</span><br><span class="line">yang --&gt; shaoyang &amp; taiyang</span><br><span class="line">yin --&gt; shaoyin &amp; taiyin</span><br><span class="line">wu[吾之利]</span><br><span class="line">wu --&gt; yang &amp; yin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>阳主入，指收入。阴主出，指支出。<br>阳分少阳，分太阳。少阳分巽，分坎。太阳分兑，分乾。<br>阴分少阴，分太阴。少阴分震，分离。太阴分艮，分坤。<br>少阳为瞬。巽为瞬，为变。坎为瞬，为定。<br>太阳为恒。兑为恒，为变。乾为恒，为定。<br>少阴为往。震为往，为可。离为往，为须。<br>太阴为复。艮为复，为可。坤为复，为须。<br>瞬者，不可持续。恒者，可持可续。<br>变者，不可预期。定者，可预可期。</p><p>当取恒，取定。取复，取须。<br>瞬变应可往，瞬定应须往，恒变应可复，恒定应须复。<br>同声相应，同气相求。</p><p>瞬变者，鉴其入。瞬定者，鉴其源。<br>恒变者，鉴其危。恒定者，鉴其久。<br>可往者，用以惧。须往者，用以慎。<br>可复者，用以止。须复者，用以顺。</p>]]></content>
    
    
